Comment: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:09.53,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,{\an8}We've received a transmission from a Mr. Zucchero!
Comment: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:16.70,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,{\an8}If you're waiting for the Lagoon, please come to the ship watchhouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:14.03,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Giorno, if anyone comes \N close to the watchhouse, give me the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:18.16,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,I'll shoot whoever takes the call!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:24.17,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,But since Buccellati told me not to kill him, \N I'll avoid his vitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:25.88,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Or try to, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:28.92,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,Nobody's moved yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.59,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,No one's headed toward the watchhouse...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:33.26,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Is no one going to answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:37.01,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Is nobody waiting for the Lagoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:40.72,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,There's a transmission \N from Mr. Zucchero!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:47.90,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,No, nobody is making a move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:50.57,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,But he must be somewhere on the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:53.07,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,Is he just too cautious to answer the call?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:56.16,Narrator,Sale,0,0,0,,Did something happen, Zucchero?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.12,Narrator,Sale,0,0,0,,Calling me out like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:02.33,Narrator,Sale,0,0,0,,Is there a problem? Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:08.17,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:10.55,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,No one approached the watchhouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:16.72,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,He's there! How?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:20.39,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,This is bad! \NDoes the watchhouse have a back entrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:23.18,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,He's already inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:25.64,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,It's too dark to see his face...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:27.44,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mista hasn't realized he's in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:31.90,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,At this rate, he'll realize it's a setup\N and make a run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:33.90,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,I have to tell Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:41.16,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,What?\N The guy is coming to answer the call?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:46.67,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:49.75,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Which one of them is coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:53.30,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:55.34,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,He's not headed there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:57.38,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,He's already inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:17:58.84,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,Don't expose yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:01.97,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,He's by the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:13.94,Thoughts,Sale,0,0,0,,Isn't that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:15.94,Thoughts,Sale,0,0,0,,...part of Buccellati's team?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:19.41,Thoughts,Sale,0,0,0,,Didn't Zucchero take care of him on the yacht?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:21.49,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mista! Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:24.37,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,He's on the radio! Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:26.37,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Damn! \N He can't hear me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:29.17,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,This is better than him not noticing! {Maybe "This is preferable to him not noticing!"? - Toa} {nah, this works for GioGio -JMFW}
