Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:21.30,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Yeah! Yeah! Yeah! Yeah! {No! No! No! No! -J}{Seriously though, this doesn't need to be subbed. -J}{It does, because lines 289 and 290 in episode 8 need to be subbed! -Gyro}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:23.85,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,D-Did he get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:28.81,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Wh-Who the hell are you?!
